schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
scalar Date

## Input
input Transactioninput {
    amount: Float!,
    currencyCode: String!,
    description: String!,
    expenseType: String,
    invoiceDate: Date,
    user: String!
}

type Transaction {
    _id: ID!,
    amount: Float,
    currencyCode: String,
    description: String,
    expenseType: String,
    invoiceDate: Date,
    user: String,
    reporter: String
}

type Query {
    Transactions(limit: Int): [Transaction]
    Transaction(id: ID!): Transaction
}

type Mutation {
    addTransaction(transaction: Transactioninput): Transaction
    removeTransaction(transactionId: ID!): Transaction
    updateTransaction(transactionId: ID!): Transaction
}
